author: @Chan-zi
comment:
​@@chhavigupta5405 Ye gaana aisa h, jo kaafi deep meaning rakhta hai, typical romantic gana nhi hai ye. 
Ladka aajad hai udta panchi hai isliye ladki bhi uske isi befikre mijjaj ki vajah se usse pyaar kar baithi hai, kind of samjh lo guru and chela. Jahan ek samay par guru apne shishya ko sab kuch sikhana chahta hai lekin vo puchta bhi h, kab tak sath chloge mere to vo shishya kehra hai "jab tak tu na kahe mai hara" ye jugalbandi jo aap har bhakti kavita m dekhoge jaise – kabir, meera, bullesaah, Rumi.
Maane ye raah bhaut kathin hai, apne ahenkaar ko chod satya ki or jaane ki baat ho rhi h pure gaane me, dhyaan se sunna is baar Hero yahan ek guru h jo koi bandhan nhi manta or ladki uska discipline jo uske isi beparvaah mijaj ki vajah se bandhan todta hua aage badna chahta hai par sharir,samaj, sanyog itni aasani se aisa nhi hone deta.
